    "body": "### Problem\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/947c7f7b-882a-4716-b1de-719eb1e38563\n\nThis issue may be related to #30165\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n`minimal.lua`:\n\n```\nvim.o.autoindent = true\nvim.o.showmode = false\n\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_lines(0, 0, -1, true, {\"ab\"})\n\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\n\t{\n\t\t\"InsertLeavePre\",\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tcallback = function()\n\t\t\tvim.print(\n\t\t\t\ttable.concat(\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvim.fn.col(\".\"),\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvim.fn.virtcol(\".\"),\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvim.fn.getpos(\".\")[3],\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvim.api.nvim_win_get_cursor(0)[2],\n\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t\t\" \"\n\t\t\t\t)\n\t\t\t)\n\t\tend,\n\t}\n)\n```\n\n1. run `nvim --clean -u minimal.lua`\n2. press `li<cr><esc>`\n3. the message is `2 2 2 1`, which should be `1 1 1 0`\n4. press `i<esc>`\n5. the message is `1 1 1 0`, which is expected\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nboth message should be `1 1 1 0`\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.11.0-dev-2016+gf5714994bc\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nnot sure\n\n### Operating system/version\n\n6.13.7-arch1-1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nst 0.8.5\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nst-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nnightly",
